      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PIZZA PRINCE (3) is yet to have his colours lowered in three runs at this circuit and distance so far this campaign, most recently getting home by 8 metres after leading from one spot wider. Up in grade but can push forward again from this advantageous draw so could go right on with the job. SASSY GALLEON (2) has added to a series of wins and placings by scoring in her last two outings here. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run and she strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance. Big chance to land the hat trick. CALL ME TROUBLE NZ (7) continued his consistent form when placed here last week. Go well again. MAJESTIC BREEZE NZ (9) broke and finished a long way back last start but won twice in a row at this circuit and distance prior so is worth another chance. KODA DA MODA (5) progressed off a fresh placing to win last start. In form and could go on with it.",
